name: Feena Fam Earthlight LoRa
description:
A character from Brighter Than the Dawning Blue (夜明け前より瑠璃色な)

Dress

Tiara, Blue dress, White puffy sleeves, white long gloves, white skirt

Sundress

Sundress, Straw Hat

School Uniform

White School uniform, Blue pleated skirt, zettai ryouiki, white thighhighs, green bow

*Below messages are for V1.x*

Consist of 2 versions trained separately.

- 1.0, Got the color of the dress right, but sometimes gives incorrect face proportion.

- 1.5, Accurate face proportion, somehow need more weight to get the dress colors right.

Combine both versions [0.5,0.5] give a surprisingly good result

Trained with a merged model of 7th Anime + Anything + AOM.

But should work well with other models

"Ligne Claire" prompt is recommended to match the original's aesthetic.

Sample for the prompt I used

<lora:Feena_Local:1>,<lora:Feena-000008:0.5>,Anime drawing of Feena, Crown, Green Eyes, light purple hair, long hair, long white skirt, white gloves, puffy sleeves, ligne claire, cleavage, (blue:1.5) dress, solo

Feena-000008 = V1.0

Feena_Local = V1.5

Character name is not required to trigger the LoRa.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
• Re-train with more images.

  • No longer needs to combine LORAs.

  • Sundress / Maid / School uniform can now be generated with questionable reliability

It doesn't require trigger words, but to correctly generate each costume requires additional prompts
